## This file is bundled with the app (Flutter assets).
## Configure the backend API base URL here.
##
## Phone over USB (recommended):
## 1) Run backend on your PC (example: localhost:5003)
## 2) Run: adb reverse tcp:5003 tcp:5003
## 3) Keep this as:
##    API_BASE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:5003
##
## Same Wiâ€‘Fi LAN:
## - Use your PC LAN IP and a backend port that binds to 0.0.0.0 (example 5002):
##   API_BASE_URL=http://192.168.1.11:5002
API_BASE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:5003


